Class ModuleInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.jandex.ModuleInfo

  • public final class ModuleInfo
extends Object
    Represents a module descriptor entry in an index.

    Thread-Safety

    This class is immutable and can be shared between threads without safe publication.
